00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,480
Come here.

10
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,160
Look.

11
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,160
It's finally

12
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,960
snowing.

13
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:58,840
Did I go too far

14
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,960
with Lord Zhang today?

15
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,720
You can't possibly

16
