acting like a spy for him.

18
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,880
Eventually, this will come to an end.

19
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,480
But today,

20
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,680
you brought up the Shens' case.

21
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,280
Did you uncover

22
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,200
