all the clues are tangled and confusing,

29
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:32,080
and we still can't be entirely sure.

30
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,000
But one thing is clear,

31
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,280
that long before the Shens' incident,

32
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,000
there were multiple forces

33
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,520
beginning to plot behind the scenes.

34
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,680
I have a feeling.

35
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:43,680
What is it?

36
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,520
I was thinking,

37
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,640
the situation your father was in back then

38
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:51,520
is not too different from yours now.

39
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,960
I mean,

40
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,280
navigating among various fractions,

41
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,120
to stay impartial while keeping

42
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,440
dignity is no easy task.

43
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,440
A small misstep could lead to...

44
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,640
A fallen tree attracts many axes.

45
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,840
Staying true to yourself is right.

46
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,200
And it's also not wrong to avoid

47
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,160
bowing down to the powerful.

48
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,920
Shen Du.

49
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:16,360
Please keep doing what you do,

50
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,560
and pursue what you desire.

51
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,520
I will do my utmost

52
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,240
to help you uncover the truth,

53
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,200
and clear the name of the Shen Family.

54
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,760
Snow on the winter solstice

55
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,840
is a sign of a fruitful year ahead.

56
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,680
Lord Commander is nothing special.

57
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,480
Let's see

58
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,840
if you can catch me.

59
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:35,360
Poker face, poker face!

60
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,560
Come on!

61
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,280
Chui!

62
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,320
Hurry!

63
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:43,400
How are you? Are you cold?

64
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,480
Absolutely freezing!

65
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:45,679
Feeling any better?

66
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,360
What were you doing?

67
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,640
I went to buy you some treat.

68
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:05,600
[Try it.]

69
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:18,920
It's good.

70
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,000
Slow down.

71
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,520
Your cheeks are all puffed up.

72
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,280
It's good!

73
