578
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,200
just ask Lady Yan

579
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:34,080
and you'll find out!

580
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:34,720
Alright!

581
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:35,440
You go ask...

582
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:37,200
What are you talking about?

583
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,400
Stop bothering her!

584
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:39,560
What do you mean, my lord?

585
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:40,760
Lady Yan...

586
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:42,720
Something serious happened to her family.

587
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:43,440
You didn't know?

588
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,040
The Jins have been suspected

589
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:49,200
of inciting Prince Xian to rebel,

590
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:50,920
and the II has rounded them all up.

591
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:52,680
By the way,

592
00:32:53,360 --> 00:32:54,960
even if something major happens,

593
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,080
don't bother Lady Yan.

594
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:57,120
You're right, Lord Wu.

595
00:32:57,120 --> 00:32:58,240
I'll go find her myself.

596
00:32:58,400 --> 00:32:59,200
Farewell!

597
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:01,120
Watch your step!

598
00:33:41,600 --> 00:33:42,720
What is this place?

599
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:48,400
Everyone calls me the Dark Demon.

600
00:33:50,360 --> 00:33:51,400
So perhaps,

601
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:54,480
this is the underworld.

602
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:56,120
What do you want?

603
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:58,480
Are you going to kill me?

604
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:07,920
The eighteen layers of hell

605
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:11,080
are reserved for others.

606
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:13,320
As for you,

607
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:14,600
even if one day

608
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:15,880
you truly end up in the underworld,

609
00:34:16,200 --> 00:34:17,920
I'll use the bones as the lamp,

610
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,240
and offer evil spirits as sacrifice,

611
00:34:19,240 --> 00:34:21,000
to illuminate the King Hall of Hell

612
00:34:22,080 --> 00:34:23,040
and transform it into

613
00:34:24,160 --> 00:34:25,640
a paradise for you.

614
00:34:28,680 --> 00:34:30,240
There's no way to escape.

615
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:49,720
What's got you so scared?

616
00:35:00,359 --> 00:35:01,160
I...

617
00:35:02,279 --> 00:35:03,960
will not hurt you at all.

618
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:11,799
Chui.

619
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,279
Raise your head.

620
00:35:18,319 --> 00:35:19,120
Look around you.

621
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:20,279
What do you think?

622
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:21,839
Do you like these?

623
00:35:33,160 --> 00:35:35,040
What... is...

624
00:35:40,120 --> 00:35:41,040
Word has it that you're

625
00:35:41,040 --> 00:35:42,280
quite content with the wedding gifts

626
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:43,480
Jiang Langxing sent.

627
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:49,960
So these are the things you like.

628
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:52,920
I bought everything that girls adore

629
00:35:53,160 --> 00:35:55,040
from the market in Xiang'an,

630
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,240
[as well as all the wedding gifts]

631
00:35:57,240 --> 00:35:59,000
[that wealthy families]

632
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:00,760
use for betrothal.

633
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,360
What do you think?

634
00:36:04,320 --> 00:36:05,800
What exactly do you want?

635
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:07,440
I'm here to propose!

636
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:08,880
Propose?

637
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,600
I'm asking for your hand in marriage.

638
00:36:11,160 --> 00:36:13,040
May you agree to be my wife.

639
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:14,080
What are you talking about?

640
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:16,800
I'm already engaged to Jiang Langxing!

641
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:18,400
I'm going to marry him!

642
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:21,960
That rigid delinquent,

643
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,320
what's so special about him?

644
00:36:24,120 --> 00:36:25,120
What he offers,

645
00:36:25,120 --> 00:36:26,760
I can give you ten times more.

646
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:28,160
[This isn't about that.]

647
00:36:29,080 --> 00:36:30,760
I've already promised to marry him.

648
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:39,560
What's so significant about a promise?

649
00:36:40,200 --> 00:36:42,360
Even if you are wed, you can still divorce.

650
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:52,080
If you feel guilty towards him,

651
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:54,400
I can make it up to him for you.

652
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:56,800
As long as he likes,

653
00:36:57,880 --> 00:36:59,720
I could take out Xu Xiangren

654
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:02,080
and make him the Chief Inspector.

655
00:37:02,080 --> 00:37:03,160
Don't pull any mad stunts!

656
00:37:07,120 --> 00:37:07,920
Alright.

657
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,600
I'll do as you say.

658
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,680
Why can't you see?

659
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:16,960
Jiang Langxing and I

660
00:37:17,160 --> 00:37:18,680
have genuine feelings for each other.

661
00:37:18,720 --> 00:37:20,320
We have feelings for each other too!

662
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:21,760
I like you a lot!

663
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:22,840
I've never cared for a woman

664
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:24,080
as deeply as I care for you!

665
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,800
But I don't like you!

666
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,720
That's a lie!

667
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:28,080
You clearly have feelings for me too!

668
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,560
Didn't you call me maskman

669
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:33,200
and treat me like a close friend?

670
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:34,400
Also...

671
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:35,520
Our mothers

672
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:36,760
are buried in the same spot.

673
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,560
This is destiny for sure!

674
00:37:38,560 --> 00:37:40,000
The affection between friends

675
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:41,000
is different from

676
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:42,320
that of lovers.

677
00:37:42,600 --> 00:37:44,280
I have no such feelings for you!

678
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:45,680
That's not possible!

679
00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:47,000
It won't be long before

680
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,440
you realize I'm right.

681
00:38:05,520 --> 00:38:06,560
Let go of me!

682
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:23,120
It's alright.

683
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:26,120
I'm willing to wait;

684
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:28,600
eventually,

685
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,080
you'll fall in love with me.

686
00:39:55,160 --> 00:39:55,960
Stop right there!

687
00:39:56,240 --> 00:39:57,280
[The case of Jin Family's usurpation is]

688
00:39:57,280 --> 00:39:59,000
entirely under the jurisdiction of Il.

689
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,720
The Ministry of Justice can't interfere.

690
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:01,640
[Lady Yan,]

691
00:40:01,680 --> 00:40:02,480
[please leave.]

692
00:40:04,120 --> 00:40:04,920
Hold on.

693
00:40:07,680 --> 00:40:08,480
Greetings, my lord.

694
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:09,760
[Lady Yan,]

695
00:40:10,240 --> 00:40:11,240
[if you want to save your family,]

696
00:40:11,240 --> 00:40:12,520
[it's actually quite simple.]

697
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,120
You just need to submit a petition

698
00:40:14,680 --> 00:40:16,120
[stating that the Jin Family]

699
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:18,160
was falsely accused by Shen Du.

700
00:40:18,240 --> 00:40:19,720
Then I can help you overturn the case

701
00:40:20,080 --> 00:40:21,720
and rescue your family.

702
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,360
Lord Lai,

703
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:27,960
you're deliberately teasing me.

704
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:29,800
I won't betray my husband

705
00:40:30,200 --> 00:40:31,320
with false charges.

706
00:40:32,520 --> 00:40:33,560
I didn't realize

707
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:35,720
that the former spy

708
00:40:35,720 --> 00:40:37,600
who married into the Shen Family

709
00:40:38,040 --> 00:40:39,360
[would now be so deeply]

710
00:40:39,840 --> 00:40:42,080
in love with Shen Du.

711
00:40:42,240 --> 00:40:43,120
Lord Lai,

712
00:40:43,960 --> 00:40:45,520
there's no need to

713
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:46,480
use my past as leverage.

714
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:47,640
[Regarding this,]

715
00:40:47,960 --> 00:40:48,840
[I have already explained everything to]

716
00:40:48,840 --> 00:40:50,360
[my husband and Lord Zhang.]

717
00:40:50,720 --> 00:40:52,200
My conscience is clear

718
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:53,200
and have not

719
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:54,840
wronged anyone.

720
00:40:55,160 --> 00:40:56,320
[I have been diligent in my duties]

721
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:57,480
[at the Ministry of Justice,]

722
00:40:58,000 --> 00:41:00,000
committed to uncovering the truth

723
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:01,840
and clearing the names of the wronged.

724
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:03,840
Not to mention that Shen Du is my husband,

725
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,920
even if it were anyone else,

726
00:41:06,080 --> 00:41:07,160
I, Yan Xing,

727
00:41:07,160 --> 00:41:08,600
would never do anything

728
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:09,160
to tarnish my reputation

729
00:41:09,160 --> 00:41:10,840
as a Ministry of Justice official!

730
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:13,760
Lady Yan, there's no need to be stubborn.

731
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:15,760
[One day,]

732
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:17,480
you will yield to me.

733
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,160
Lady Yan,

734
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,240
please leave.

735
00:41:27,680 --> 00:41:28,320
Please!

736
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:02,520
Xing.

737
00:42:09,800 --> 00:42:10,600
Welcome back.

738
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:12,760
Xing,

739
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:17,240
Her Royal Highness hasn't budged.

740
00:42:18,680 --> 00:42:20,040
I will think of another way.

741
00:42:21,840 --> 00:42:22,920
I already foresaw it.

742
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:25,200
I went to see Lord Zhang today

743
00:42:25,680 --> 00:42:27,000
and gained some insight

744
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,400
into Her Royal Highness' difficulties.

745
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:31,920
Even though I don't attend the assembly,

746
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:34,360
I could envision the situation back then.

747
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:36,240
If Lai Luozhi succeeds

748
00:42:36,600 --> 00:42:37,720
in framing Prince Xian

749
00:42:37,720 --> 00:42:39,200
with these accusations,

750
00:42:40,520 --> 00:42:41,440
it wouldn't just mean

751
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:43,160
the annihilation of the Jin Family,

752
00:42:43,240 --> 00:42:44,640
but a complete upheaval in the court.

753
00:42:45,160 --> 00:42:46,320
There would be fierce power struggles.

754
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,440
I can't imagine how many families

755
00:42:53,440 --> 00:42:54,520
would face destruction...

756
00:42:55,440 --> 00:42:56,560
I will find another way.

757
00:43:00,240 --> 00:43:01,040
Tomorrow, the Jin Family

758
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:04,480
will be put on public display

759
00:43:04,480 --> 00:43:05,480
by the Imperial Inspectorate.

760
00:43:08,520 --> 00:43:10,040
After that, there may still be hope.

